tika.dc.description: The infamous bounty hunter known as Iron Eyes finally manages to catch up with outlaw Dan Creedy. With his usual deadly resolve, Iron Eyes would have dispatched Creedy and claimed the reward. Yet this time it was different for, at last, he had met a man who was almost his equal. The seriously wounded Iron Eyes rides off towards the forest, but he has no idea Creedy's three outlaw brothers are now hunting him. For the first time in his life, it is Iron Eyes who is the prey...
